sys_hub_action_type_definition.description:
Ingests a document with the given properties into the batcher.

Inputs:

  • External Content Table - Name of the table that represents the schema of the document.
  • Document ID - Unique identifier of the document.
  • Properties - JSON containing the map of the properties related to the document.
  • Batcher ID - Unique identifier of the batcher.
  • Principals - JSON containing the map of Principals

Outputs:

  • Status - If the request is executed successfully, Status is set to "Success". If there is a failure, Status is set to "Error".
  • Error Message - Reason for error. Populated only when an error occurs.

Error Messages:

  • Invalid external content table.
  • Invalid Document ID.
  • Invalid Batcher ID.
  • Invalid properties.
  • Invalid Principals.
  • Error occurred while ingesting properties into the batcher.
  • Encountered an error. Check log for more details.

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More

sys_hub_action_type_snapshot.description:
Ingests a document with the given properties into the batcher.

Inputs:

  • External Content Table - Name of the table that represents the schema of the document.
  • Document ID - Unique identifier of the document.
  • Properties - JSON containing the map of the properties related to the document.
  • Batcher ID - Unique identifier of the batcher.
  • Principals - JSON containing the map of Principals

Outputs:

  • Status - If the request is executed successfully, Status is set to "Success". If there is a failure, Status is set to "Error".
  • Error Message - Reason for error. Populated only when an error occurs.

Error Messages:

  • Invalid external content table.
  • Invalid Document ID.
  • Invalid Batcher ID.
  • Invalid properties.
  • Invalid Principals.
  • Error occurred while ingesting properties into the batcher.
  • Encountered an error. Check log for more details.

Note: Requires a subscription for production use. Read More
